do we need more than one model? 
User information for login/logout: 
    username, String
    email, String
    password, String

Registrant Collection: { 
    firstName: {
        type: String, 
        trim: true, 
        required: 'Must enter a first name', 
    },
    lastName: {
        type: String, 
        trim: true, 
        required: 'Must enter a last name', 
    }, 
    email: {
        type: String, 
        trim: true, 
        required: 'Must enter a valid email address', 
    }, 
    title: {
        type: String, 
        trim: true, 
    } 


Certificate information for User/Certificate: 
date issued, 
issued to, 
for what purpose, 
by whom, 
witness, 
signature *  
